{"tid":1692950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[需要廣泛文宣] 必須解釋民主制度點樣防止警暴","createTime":"2019-11-04T10:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T07:35:56.000Z","uid":173326,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"01d48f13dc51a1229a61ef0aeead07d7b3ae6f2c","tid":1692950,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:37:17.000Z","msg":"6.9 百二萬人為左反送中<br />\n6.16 二百萬人為左反送中、反警暴<br />\n<br />\n之後暫停送中其實有啲攰嘅人已經收貨，至今最大嘅社會不滿係警暴、濫權問題。<br />\n<br />\n港豬會天真以為中央下次欽點個冇咁鷹派嘅特首有、政府獨立調查今次警暴，就唔會再有下次。<br />\n<br />\n佢地從來都冇思考過點樣預防警暴，更加冇諗過民主制度(例如真普選) 可以防止再有暴政利用黑警欺壓市民。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以文宣有兩大重點：<br />\n1. 說明極權同警暴兩者嘅必然關係，附加德國納粹、明代東廠等例子<br />\n2. 說明民主制度如何預防、制止執法者濫用權力剝奪市民人權自由</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"71297083420ed3fa762e3a7cf18a63159c45a91f","tid":1692950,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"推 順便借位<br />\n<br />\n【認真參考日本社運】想行得遠過藍絲，不如唔好再鬧同路人啲ig？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692734</a>"},{"pid":"060531d971e63ff4829c2b3e80098b86846bca75","tid":1692950,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146940fdecd102af65ee8dbcb6e73ef4f73eef86","tid":1692950,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74878f85f49aca0ed38bc1ded2ec87c36bcf68a8","tid":1692950,"uid":6372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"95896ffbb5c979f8db0718c867e71930aee7d1f9","tid":1692950,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img 